Class HatchBrush

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mindfusion.drawing.Brush
      • com.mindfusion.drawing.HatchBrush
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class HatchBrush
extends Brush
    Represents a brush that fills the interiors of objects with a hatch pattern.
